<mhw>

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: shrinkwrap
<hw>shrink"wrap</hw></mhw>, <pos>n.</pos>
<def>a type of plastic film, usually transparent, that shrinks upon
application of heat, and may be used to form a wrapping around objects
that fits tightly and closely follows the contours of the wrapped
object; -- also called <altname>shrink-pack</altname>,
<altname>shrinkpack</altname> or
<altname>shrink-wrapping</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Shrivalty</ent>⟦br⟧
